<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en-US">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta http-equiv="X-UA-Compatible" content="IE=edge">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Airpax - Trip Confirmation Failed Email</title>
    <style type="text/css">
        /* Client-specific styles */
        body, table, td, a { -webkit-text-size-adjust: 100%; -ms-text-size-adjust: 100%; }
        table, td { mso-table-lspace: 0pt; mso-table-rspace: 0pt; }
        img { -ms-interpolation-mode: bicubic; border: 0; height: auto; line-height: 100%; outline: none; text-decoration: none; }
        
        /* Reset styles */
        body { margin: 0 !important; padding: 0 !important; width: 100% !important; }
        
        /* iOS BLUE LINKS */
        a[x-apple-data-detectors] {
            color: inherit !important;
            text-decoration: none !important;
            font-size: inherit !important;
            font-family: inherit !important;
            font-weight: inherit !important;
            line-height: inherit !important;
        }
        
        /* Main styles */
        body {
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            background-color: #f4f4f4;
            color: #333;
            line-height: 1.5;
        }
        
        .email-container {
            max-width: 600px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            padding: 20px;
            background-color: #fff;
        }
        
        h2 {
            color: #2a9d8f;
            margin-top: 0;
            text-align: center;
        }
        
        p {
            font-size: 16px;
            margin-bottom: 16px;
        }
        
        .content-block {
            padding: 0 20px;
            max-width: 600px;
            margin: 0 auto;
        }
        
        .details-table {
            width: 100%;
            border-collapse: collapse;
            margin: 20px 0;
            font-size: 14px;
        }
        
        .details-table th,
        .details-table td {
            text-align: left;
            padding: 10px;
            border-bottom: 1px solid #ddd;
        }
        
        .details-table th {
            background-color: #f0f0f0;
            color: #333;
            width: 30%;
        }
        
        .footer {
            text-align: center;
            font-size: 12px;
            color: #666;
            margin-top: 30px;
            padding-top: 20px;
            border-top: 1px solid #eee;
        }
        
        .footer p {
            margin: 5px 0;
            font-size: 12px;
        }
        
        /* Responsive styles */
        @media screen and (max-width: 600px) {
            .email-container {
                width: 100% !important;
                padding: 10px !important;
            }
            .content-block {
                padding: 0 10px !important;
            }
            .details-table th,
            .details-table td {
                display: block;
                width: 100% !important;
                box-sizing: border-box;
            }
            .details-table th {
                background-color: transparent;
                padding-bottom: 0;
            }
            .details-table tr {
                margin-bottom: 15px;
                display: block;
            }
        }
    </style>
</head>

<body style="margin: 0; padding: 0;">
    <!-- Email wrapper -->
    <table role="presentation" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0" border="0" align="center" width="100%" style="max-width: 600px;">
        <tr>
            <td bgcolor="#ffffff">
                <!--[if mso]>
                <table role="presentation" align="center" border="0" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0" width="600">
                <tr>
                <td>
                <![endif]-->
                
                <div class="email-container">
                    <div class="content-block">
                        <h2>Payment Failed â€“ Your Trip Details</h2>
                        <p>Dear <strong><%= user %></strong>,</p>
                        <p>We regret to inform you that your trip has been canceled. Below are the details of your canceled booking. If you have any questions or require further assistance, please don't hesitate to contact our support team.</p>
                        
                        <h3 style="margin-bottom: 10px;">Trip Details:</h3>
                        <table class="details-table">
                            <tr>
                                <th>From</th>
                                <td><%= trip.from %></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th>To</th>
                                <td><%= trip.to %></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th>Journey Start Date</th>
                                <td><%= trip.journeystartdate %></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th>Journey End Date</th>
                                <td><%= trip.journeyenddate %></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th>Journey Start Time</th>
                                <td><%= trip.starttime %></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th>Journey End Time</th>
                                <td><%= trip.endtime %></td>
                            </tr>
                        </table>

                        <h3 style="margin-bottom: 10px;">Ticket Information:</h3>
                        <table class="details-table">
                            <tr>
                                <th>PNR Number</th>
                                <td><strong><%= payment.pnr %></strong></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th>Total Amount</th>
                                <td><%= payment.amount %></td>
                            </tr>
                        </table>

                        <h3 style="margin-bottom: 10px;">Passenger Details:</h3>
                        <% seat.forEach(function(seat) { %>
                        <table class="details-table" style="margin-bottom: 20px;">
                            <tr>
                                <th>First Name</th>
                                <td><%=seat.details.fname %></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th>Last Name</th>
                                <td><%=seat.details.lname %></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th>Age</th>
                                <td><%=seat.details.age %></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th>Gender</th>
                                <td><%=seat.details.gender %></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th>Email</th>
                                <td><%=seat.details.email %></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th>Phone No</th>
                                <td><%=seat.details.mobileno %></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th>Seat No</th>
                                <td><%=seat.seatNumber %></td>
                            </tr>
                        </table>
                        <% }); %>

                        <p>If you need any further assistance, please feel free to contact us at <a href="mailto:info@airpax.co">info@airpax.co</a> or call us at <a href="tel:+919990301111">+919990301111</a>. You can also visit our website <a href="https://airpax.co/">Airpax</a> for more information.</p>

                        <p>We wish you a pleasant and enjoyable trip!</p>

                        <p>Best regards,</p>
                        <p><strong>Airpax</strong></p>
                    </div>
                    
                    <div class="footer">
                        <p><strong>RIGI TRANS TECH PVT LTD</strong></p>
                        <p>PERNAM INN 837/1</p>
                        <p>MANDI ESTATE, NEW DELHI</p>
                        <p>110047</p>
                        <p>Email: <a href="mailto:info@airpax.co">info@airpax.co</a> | Phone: <a href="tel:+919990301111">+919990301111</a></p>
                        <p><a href="https://www.airpax.co/">www.airpax.co</a></p>
                    </div>
                </div>
                
                <!--[if mso]>
                </td>
                </tr>
                </table>
                <![endif]-->
            </td>
        </tr>
    </table>
</body>
</html>